title: The Baltimore Bullet - Very rare DVD-R
description:
Another Rarekoala release!!


The Baltimore Bullet, a 1980 comedy about two pool hustlers on the road, out to score big.

Starring James Coburn and Omar Sherrif

Never released on DVD!!!!


*** This is a convert from an old VHS tape. ***  As such, the quality is not that of a DVD, or a perfect VHS tape, however it is quite watchable.  It appeared fuzzy on my PC, but quality improved upon playing on TV.  There is a bit of line artifact in the early part of the film, but clears up quickly.


A Pirate Bay exclusive!! (for now).  The *only* copy available as a torrent!!
